<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MuTA76">
<l>poruppiṭaiyē niṉṟum puṉalkuḷittu maintu</l>
<l>neruppiṭaiyē niṟkavunīr vēṇṭā – viruppuṭaiya</l>
<l>veḵkāvē cērntāṉai meymmalartūyk kaitoḻutā</l>
<l>laḵkāvē tīviṉaika ḷāyntu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Not wanting to stand on heights, bathe in floods and stand</l>
<l>midst the five fires, if you truly strew blossoms [and] fold</l>
<l>[your] hands in worship to the one who joined desirable Veḵkā,</l>
<l>[your] evil deeds will dwindle [and] pass away.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
